Didn't it used to have an HP regen that stacked with Marr?<br>
If not and you are 65 it seems kind of a waste of a song slot to me.<br>
<br>
Reguardless of the situation (exp or MT raid) I would skip Niv's.<br>
<br>
The AC on Niv's isn't going to make or break the tank and the rune effect doesn't appear to be melee based.  Besides its too small to do much good anyway. <br>
- For an LDoN or exp grind I'd stick with riz/muse, zek, marr &amp; Veeshan.  <br>
