- If you have a mob that flurries or can't be slowed the DS from zek &amp; Veeshan is much better. <br>
- in a MT group a charisma boost for Divine Intervention would be handy<br>
<br>
One cautionary note:<br>
Niv's and Shield of Songs both have a Rune type effect.  I think the SoS one used to have stacking problems with enchanters Rune line - prevented rune from landing.   Not sure if it still does or not. (I think I wiped a VSR raid by accident once this way.) Since then I shelved both of these two songs.<br>
